text.section: This title does not limit the right of an individual to practice a health occupation that the individual is authorized to practice under this article.
This title does not limit the right of a physician authorized under Title 14 of this article to perform acupuncture as it is defined in that title.
This title does not limit a dentist licensed under Title 4 of this article who is authorized to perform acupuncture in connection with the practice of dentistry.
This title does not limit a veterinarian licensed under the Agriculture Article who performs acupuncture on animals in connection with the practice of veterinary medicine.
